{"tid":1124382,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"望住香港，有時候真係好心酸","createTime":"2019-04-25T04:11:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-26T03:26:46.000Z","uid":137335,"like":33,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"a490c91c0f7d0d0061b894886adbcc6eec564db1","tid":1124382,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:11:42.000Z","msg":"生於斯，長於斯<br />\n<br />\n政府都會不斷宣傳 家是香港<br />\n<br />\n好多成就會令我哋作為一個香港人而自豪<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n特別有時聽到政府嘅宣傳歌<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/RkcT0B-Vh8Y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FRkcT0B-Vh8Y&d=sSksRl51obRI29wW5WU5SWg5BW3O7pEdz%2F%2BecHjXtrw%3D&h=bede5507\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/RkcT0B-Vh8Y</a><br />\n<br />\n<code>因此知道珍惜我的香港\n因此懂去欣賞我的香港</code><br />\n<br />\n就會諗係咪好多人係我哋日常習慣咗就唔知我哋嘅優點<br />\n<br />\n土地問題無可否認係大問題，但其他呢？<br />\n<br />\n我哋雖然地方細，但城市郊區我哋都有<br />\n<br />\n有啲人會專登飛去奈良撚鹿<br />\n但唔會去馬騮山撚馬騮<br />\n<br />\n同一場雨，深圳死幾個人，香港可以咩事冇<br />\n<br />\n其他地方住市郊慘過食兩舊屎，香港可以半個鐘出到市區<br />\n<br />\n香港電力好穩定，去過澳洲嘅巴絲都知嗰邊間唔中又停下電或者電壓唔穩<br />\n<br />\n仲有好多好多數之不盡嘅野<br />\n<br />\n睇到有個90後移民post好心酸<br />\n<br />\n我有能力移民，但我唔會移民，因為我只想令自己嘅屋企變好<br />\n<br />\n香港雖然一步一步沉緊，但係唔代表就咁就走，香港始終係我哋嘅家，比班強國人入侵佔領你哋唔通又甘心咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e92772ad349941f49ab1da6b01c3befe785c1536","tid":1124382,"uid":138197,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"冇計 政府帶頭出賣港人"},{"pid":"b3b77f47f67409f44a2369e169c32fad27619796","tid":1124382,"uid":10679,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:36:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a91c0ad4c25ff425424aae76bb17ae48207fff3f","tid":1124382,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e92772ad349941f49ab1da6b01c3befe785c1536","tid":1124382,"uid":138197,"like":12,"dislike":1,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:20:48.000Z","msg":"冇計 政府帶頭出賣港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T04:42:11.000Z","msg":"以前政府嘅努力<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />比97後嘅港共<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"197cc5e8cc4b20120a1990bdfb96618c8d311f87","tid":1124382,"uid":137335,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T11:44:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n而家連AWS都嚟香港開Data center<br />\n反而到我哋走<br />\n<br />\n咁樣好咩<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66d89d8763ccb0a5e8b9cf43f3d08dce03716bc3","tid":1124382,"uid":9193,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-25T11:46:46.000Z","msg":"只要繼續有150 我地做乜都冇用"},{"pid":"5fefe1d8457c4597e5b8ae667372f9803ce7e6d4","tid":1124382,"uid":28603,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:49:25.000Z","msg":"屌你，咁你寧願成世人幫地產商打工定係間中停下電？"},{"pid":"ec793185c067bf64cd46a32117e26e205a7f3753","tid":1124382,"uid":136625,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:51:19.000Z","msg":"都係果句 香港呢塊福地留番比你地啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"33ff7b214bc4ac1ea10384aa14ed660798a75764","tid":1124382,"uid":247923,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T00:54:38.000Z","msg":"為何要留咁多好野俾新香港人?<br />\n我已經無下一代,將來係點關我叉事"},{"pid":"707bfc294a44a9bfdf2d22f2ecbfc9fa2af33f72","tid":1124382,"uid":235652,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:35:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"127288d6a12044e070522e92a9cdd7faade0a96a","tid":1124382,"uid":215833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-26T02:56:12.000Z","msg":"連高官d仔女都拎外國護照同係外國讀書,香港人仲點愛香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b02d66ee898